  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK874">
<l>pakainaṭpāk koṇṭoḻukum paṇpuṭai yāḷaṉ </l>
<l>ṟakaimaikkaṭ ṭaṅku mulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world abides in the greatness of that good-natured man who behaves so as to turn hatred into friendship.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
